            <p className="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Downforce consistency measures how stable your aerodynamic platform remains as speed changes. In simple terms: does the car produce proportional downforce at 100 kph as it does at 250 kph? Does the balance between front and rear stay predictable?
            </p>
            <p className="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
