              <div className="text-sm text-gray-700">Car feels planted and predictable. Driver can commit fully to every corner knowing the aerodynamic platform will support them.</div>
            </div>
            <div className="bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <div className="font-bold text-red-900 mb-2">Poor Consistency</div>
              <div className="text-sm text-gray-700">Car feels nervous or unpredictable. Driver hesitates, loses confidence, and cannot extract maximum performance.</div>
            </div>
          </div>

