            <h4 className="font-bold text-lg mb-3">The Competitive Reality</h4>
            <p className="text-sm mb-3">
              Teams that cannot manage ride height variations face impossible choices:
            </p>
            <div className="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <div className="flex items-start">
                <span className="mr-3">→</span>
                <span>Run car high: Lose 3-5% downforce everywhere, surrendering 0.3-0.5s per lap</span>
              </div>
              <div className="flex items-start">
                <span className="mr-3">→</span>
                <span>Run car low: Risk floor damage, porpoising, and unpredictable handling</span>
              </div>
              <div className="flex items-start">
                <span className="mr-3">→</span>
                <span>Compromise setup: Give away performance in multiple areas</span>
              </div>
            </div>
